<li><a href="news://alt.fan.james-burke" class="external text" title="news://alt.fan.james-burke" rel="nofollow">Burke's fans newsgroup</a></li>
<li><a href="http://tv.groups.yahoo.com/group/connectionswithjamesburke/" class="external text" title="http://tv.groups.yahoo.com/group/connectionswithjamesburke/" rel="nofollow">Yahoo group for Burke's fans</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.documentary-video.com/items.cfm?id=854" class="external text" title="http://www.documentary-video.com/items.cfm?id=854" rel="nofollow">Documentary-Video</a> where the <i>Connections</i> series and <i>The Day the Universe Changed</i> are available for sale</li>
<li><i><a href="http://www.kcsm.org/tv/catalog/Reconnections/index.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.kcsm.org/tv/catalog/Reconnections/index.htm" rel="nofollow">Re-Connections</a></i> on Burke's corpus of work, as well as an introduction to his Knowledge Web project.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.stranova.com/Podcasts/Stranova25.mp3" class="external text" title="http://www.stranova.com/Podcasts/Stranova25.mp3" rel="nofollow">Stranova Interview with James Burke on "The Knowledge Web"</a> 26 September 2006.</li>
</ul>


